1️⃣ Update Termux first
Open Termux and run:


pkg update && pkg upgrade

2️⃣ Install basic tools
These help you install other security tools.

pkg install git
pkg install python
pkg install wget
pkg install curl

3️⃣ Install a cybersecurity tooscanning 

pkg install nmap

Check version:

nmap --version

4️⃣  Install a penetration testing framework

pkg install unstable-repo
pkg install metasploit

Run it:

msfconsole